Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:12.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:15.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わっ 本当だ 膨らんだ！
Dialogue: 9,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re right!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s swelling up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャ～ッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んっ…\Nグオ～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:57.73,TS-Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.8\an4\fad(947,0)\pos(800.000000,358.000000)}FROM\NTHE\NNEW\NWORLD
Dialogue: 9,0:01:04.71,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソ…
Dialogue: 9,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:09.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:18.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ… 風船犬の…
Dialogue: 9,0:01:15.93,0:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this part of the blowdog?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m pretty sure it’s a bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:20.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,骨だよ きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソだろ…
Dialogue: 9,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re kidding me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何してんの？
Dialogue: 9,0:01:26.56,0:01:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:31.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか\N花火みたいな においがする
Dialogue: 9,0:01:28.31,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda smells like fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:34.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか なるほどね
Dialogue: 9,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:39.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… 本当に殺すためだけに\N進化するなんて あるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:01:36.20,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So some creatures really evolve just to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:44.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,種は 生き残るためなら\N何だってするんだよ…
Dialogue: 9,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They do whatever it takes for their species to survive.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:57.68,0:01:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季…
Dialogue: 9,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let’s get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:10.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく 引き返そう\Nここに固まってても絶好の的だ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re sitting ducks here.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… どうするの！\N呪力がないのに どうするの
Dialogue: 9,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re helpless without our Canti!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:26.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シ～ッ！\Nアイツらは まだ分かんねえってば
Dialogue: 9,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh. They don’t know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:30.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げ腰んところ見せたら\N調子にのって追ってくるぞ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If we start running away now,
Dialogue: 9,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they’ll get confident and start chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも ここにいたら\Nやっぱり襲われちゃうよ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But they’ll attack us anyway if we just stand here!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let’s run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:37.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうよ 逃げよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイツら\N絶対に 戦いたがってないと思う
Dialogue: 9,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m pretty sure they don’t want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちに帰ってもらいたいだけよ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They just want to drive us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？ じゃ アイツらが帰れよ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They should walk away, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと 向こうに巣穴があるのよ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Their nest must be on the far side.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.03,TS-EpTitle5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,0)\alpha&H30&\fs120.000000\blur1.54\pos(636.000000,176.000000)\c&H251343&}Pursuit on a Hot Night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.03,TS-EpTitle5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,0)\bord8.000000\alpha&H50&\1a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\fs120.000000\blur7\pos(636.000000,176.000000)\3c&H873237&}Pursuit on a Hot Night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちが怖がってると\N思わせるのも まずいから…
Dialogue: 9,0:02:59.90,0:03:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re screwed if they think we’re afraid, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆっくりな ゆっくり
Dialogue: 9,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly! Do it slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこで戦いたくないみたいだ
Dialogue: 9,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They don’t seem to want to fight over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり 巣穴があったんだな
Dialogue: 9,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that’s where their nest is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんでしょう
Dialogue: 9,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:17.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 十分\N巣穴から遠ざかったら どうなるか
Dialogue: 9,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if we get far enough from their nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワァイオ…
Dialogue: 9,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ 走れ！\Nギッグギ～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,固まるな バラバラに
Dialogue: 9,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t stick together! Split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガッガガガガ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:02.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや… 死にたくない
Dialogue: 9,0:03:59.92,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t wanna die…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季 大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 9,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚… うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 9,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t get up…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理みたい あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ… えい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走れる？
Dialogue: 9,0:04:41.96,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ… 筑波山…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Mount Tsukuba?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 歩こう
Dialogue: 9,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let’s walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううん… もう 遅いわ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it’s too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 言ってるんだよ… うっ…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:18.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガッガガガガ…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The others got away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな… たぶん逃げたよね
Dialogue: 9,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん たぶんな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガッガガガ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ… しゃべんなってか フッ…\N覚…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So we’re not allowed to talk?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫\N殺すなら とっくにやってる
Dialogue: 9,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If they wanted to kill us, they would’ve long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:38.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コイツら\N今日 初めて呪力を見たんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was the first time they saw Cantus in action.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn’t simply—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら簡単には うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚！
Dialogue: 9,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら… 殺さない…
Dialogue: 9,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He didn’t kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガッガガガ…
Dialogue: 9,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re in a real bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう ホント最低
Dialogue: 9,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How’s your wound, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚 ケガは？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然 何ともないよ\N血も乾いてるし…
Dialogue: 9,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing, I’m telling you.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood’s dried already.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re bleeding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら ここ 血が出てる
Dialogue: 9,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ どこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら ここ
Dialogue: 9,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚
Dialogue: 9,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボノボは\N個体の緊張や ストレスが高まると
Dialogue: 9,0:07:15.91,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When stress and anxiety between individuals rise,
Dialogue: 9,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they vent it through intimate sexual behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,濃密な性的接触によって\N解消します…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:26.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同性間や 未成熟な固体の場合でも
Dialogue: 9,0:07:23.04,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This also applies to immature individuals or individuals of the same sex…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふう… 早季…
Dialogue: 9,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううん… なんでもない…
Dialogue: 9,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が したげる
Dialogue: 9,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じっとしていて
Dialogue: 9,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボノボ型の愛の社会へと\N作り替えることが急務でした…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:05.29,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They considered it their immediate duty to\Ncreate a society of love similar to that of bonobos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 9,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,…a powerful attack inhibition was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:19.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強力な攻撃抑制を\N与えることが不可欠でした
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サルなんかじゃない
Dialogue: 9,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren’t monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 9,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 違うの… ほら あれっ！
Dialogue: 9,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, it’s just… Look…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t they know what privacy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちっ 邪魔なヤツだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪力なんかなくたって\N人間には 知恵がある
Dialogue: 9,0:08:41.45,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without our Canti, we still have brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚
Dialogue: 9,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オイッ ほらっ！
Dialogue: 9,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グッ ギッダグ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに怒るなよ
Dialogue: 9,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:01.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ちっ放しで\N腹が減ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 9,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry from your long watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ…
Dialogue: 9,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that…
Dialogue: 9,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, it’s the fake egg of a haythatcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カヤノスズクリの偽卵だよ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ… バッカじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらバケネズミだって\Nそんなの食べないわよ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even queerats would eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グッ ギッガグ…！
Dialogue: 9,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t they a foreign species?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コイツら 外来種だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意外と カヤノスズクリのこと\N知らないんじゃないかって
Dialogue: 9,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they have no experience with haythatchers.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢な｣じゃないわよ
Dialogue: 9,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don’t.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll just be covered in poop and get really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フンまみれにして\N怒らせるだけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガオ…\Nえっ！
Dialogue: 9,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来てる 来てる 来てる…!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re coming! They’re coming!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってる！ うるさいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急げって！
Dialogue: 9,0:10:00.66,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急いでる！
Dialogue: 9,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう… やるしかねえ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらです 早く
Dialogue: 9,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, follow me quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く こちらへ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…\Nこちらです
Dialogue: 9,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これって バケネズミの…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t this a queerat nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おケガは ありませんか？ 神様
Dialogue: 9,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt,
Dialogue: 9,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神様？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,申し遅れました
Dialogue: 9,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse my rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:52.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 塩屋虻コロニーの\N奏上役を務めます
Dialogue: 9,0:11:47.85,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a {imperial }messenger for the Robber Fly colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スクィーラと申します
Dialogue: 9,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Squealer is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.23,TS-Intro,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.4\fs110.000000\fscx150.000000\b1\bord0.000000\c&H171318&\frz15.262\pos(723.000000,591.000000)}Fly 604
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,塩谷虻…
Dialogue: 9,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Robber Fly colony…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして 我が コロニーに\N神様が ご降臨なされるとは
Dialogue: 9,0:12:02.95,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What honor it is that you should grace our colony with your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやはや 今日は\N実に めでたき日でございます
Dialogue: 9,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is truly an auspicious day.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:10.66,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have two young and beautiful gods as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それもお美しい若神様が ２柱も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か 聞こえない？
Dialogue: 9,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の音かしら
Dialogue: 9,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:31.48,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The queen is eagerly awaiting your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女王も お２人の到着を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今や遅しと 待っております
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴゴ… グオ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グガ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アア… グオ…
Dialogue: 9,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnEtruscan\fs36.000000}Gods, you honor us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:07.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガゥイサァ…\Nオヤイ… デンデドデウオ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴーヴェイ… デス…
Dialogue: 9,0:13:08.22,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnEtruscan\fs36.000000}with your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらこそ\N女王様に お目通りできて
Dialogue: 9,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The honor is ours.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:17.06,0:13:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We are delighted to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うれしく思っています
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グケオ… ガガ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:38.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グエ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女王は お２人を歓迎し
Dialogue: 9,0:13:45.13,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The queen welcomes you and shall\Nprovide hospitality as befits visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:50.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,客人として きょうすと\N申しております
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう…
Dialogue: 9,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:55.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 9,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グエ… ココ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャウ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グエ～ オエオ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオウ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グアエ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グア…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめて 殺さないで！
Dialogue: 9,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don’t kill him!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive Squealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:25.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スクィーラを許してあげて！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャウ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:34.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとりなし頂き\Nありがとうございました ああ…
Dialogue: 9,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for your intervention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかげで命拾いをいたしました
Dialogue: 9,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You have saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか…\Nあなたを殺す訳ないでしょう ねえ
Dialogue: 9,0:14:39.77,0:14:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she really mean to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は お２人に\Nお願い事がございますのですが…
Dialogue: 9,0:14:44.86,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Feral Spider colony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土蜘蛛コロニー
Dialogue: 9,0:15:01.75,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the foreign species that attacked you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先ほど 神様を襲った
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外来種の者どものことで\Nございます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:11.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数日前より 我々 在来種である\N塩屋虻コロニーとの間で
Dialogue: 9,0:15:07.13,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Several days ago, they declared war on us, who have been native in these parts since time untold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦闘状態に突入いたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てそうなの？
Dialogue: 9,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいえ 昨日 近隣の３つの\Nコロニーに特使をだしまして
Dialogue: 9,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:20.23,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday we sent special envoys to three\Nneighboring colonies to plead for reinforcements,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救援を要請したところなんですが\N到着するまでには
Dialogue: 9,0:15:27.03,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will take some time until they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今しばらくの時間が必要かと\N考えます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 今 攻めてこられたら\Nまずいんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 9,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can’t afford to be attacked right now?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよ！ 俺らが来なかったら\Nどうするつもりだったんだよ
Dialogue: 9,0:15:40.50,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we hadn’t come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:48.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい お二方の若神様たちが\Nおいでになったのは
Dialogue: 9,0:15:44.04,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure it is the will of the heavens that two young gods have come to save us from destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:53.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私共を破滅から救う\N天の ご意志であると心得ます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無礼を承知でお願いいたします
Dialogue: 9,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse my rudeness and hear my plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの神をも畏れぬ 土蜘蛛どもに
Dialogue: 9,0:16:02.35,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring down the iron hammer of vengeance on the Feral Spiders who fear not even the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:08.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようちょうの鉄ついを\N下されますように
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伏してお願い申し上げます
Dialogue: 9,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I implore you.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re really sorry, but we can’t do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,申し訳ないけど\Nそれは できないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:17.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕たちが\Nバケネズミに処分をくだす場合
Dialogue: 9,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We require permission to punish queerats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許可がいるんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:16:19.45,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fully aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 重々 承知でございます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:26.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが このままでは\N我々は 全滅を余儀なくされます
Dialogue: 9,0:16:22.16,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if no action is taken,\Nwe will inevitably meet our end here.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:31.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか後生です 何とぞ\Nヤツらに ささやかな打撃を
Dialogue: 9,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would strike only a modest blow at their ranks…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:38.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦いに負けたら\Nあなたたちは どうなるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:16:34.55,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose this war, what would happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女王は 処刑され
Dialogue: 9,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The queen would be executed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は 奴隷として\N一生 酷使されます
Dialogue: 9,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and we would work as slaves until we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きている限り\N家畜以下の扱いを受け
Dialogue: 9,0:16:45.60,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be treated like scum while we live,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ねば 野山に捨てられるか
Dialogue: 9,0:16:49.15,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and our corpses would be left in the hills to fertilize the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,畑の肥料となりましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 子供と バケネズミが\N出会うことは
Dialogue: 9,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason we have to keep children from meeting the queerats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,避けなきゃならないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru! Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚… 覚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだよ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:29.11,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it—
Dialogue: 9,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 9,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 土蜘蛛のヤツら…
Dialogue: 9,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be the Feral Spiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオ～！
Dialogue: 9,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember which way we came?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちから来たか 覚えてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:05.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん 合ってると思う
Dialogue: 9,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出口！
Dialogue: 9,0:18:21.20,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,An exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吸っちゃダメだ！
Dialogue: 9,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t breathe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\N逃げろ！
Dialogue: 9,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっち！
Dialogue: 9,0:18:48.19,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ググ… ガア！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ググ ガア…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うう！\Nガア！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グガ…\Nうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚 あれ！
Dialogue: 9,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空か
Dialogue: 9,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこから 外に出られる
Dialogue: 9,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get out from there.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚 早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚… どうしたの？
Dialogue: 9,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Satoru?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウソよ…
Dialogue: 9,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:44.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚！ はっ…
Dialogue: 9,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季～！
Dialogue: 9,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki!
